  (hardblock-verdicts
    (HARDBLOCK-03
      :verdict STILL-BROKEN
      :owner "marcus-or-ada"
      :evidence "all 12 book-of-code chapters have 0 ```scheme fences and total 174 bare ``` fences; regex at lib/book/tutor.js:173 still requires ```scheme; (book-of-code/run-code-block 6 1) still returns #f"
