      :evidence "./bin/motoi eval '(book-of-ml/tutor 6)' → error: unbound symbol: book-of-ml/tutor"
      :fix "install symmetric book-of-ml tutor + code-block runner OR route through generic book/tutor + book/run-code-block")

    (HARDBLOCK-23
